Ne5 15. Qg3 f5 $1 $17) 14... gxf4 15. Bxf4 ({Worse is:} 15. Nxf4 $6 Ne5) 15...
Ne5 16. Bxe5 fxe5 $132 {The game is still double-edged, but I prefer Black here.
