{[%evp 0,30,19,31,14,30,45,4,5,6,7,2,23,20,27,7,13,26,19,9,22,14,14,11,23,6,20,
4,10,-3,-3,-1,-1]} 1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6 3. b3 {This is another interesting
solid system. Instead of fighting for an opening advantage, White is trying to
