} 3. b4 Bg7 4. Bb2 O-O 5. e3 d6 {Now, White has a choice. Depending on the
circumstances, Black will either strike with ...a7-a5 or ...c7-c5.} 6. Be2 ({
In case of} 6. Nbd2 {Black can play} a5 $5 7. b5 {After this move, White's
