6. exd5 ({Harmless is} 6. Bd3 {when after} dxe4 7. Nxe4 Nxe4 8. Bxe4 c5 $11 {
the position is equal.}) ({In case of} 6. e5 $6 Ne4 {Black overtakes the
initiative. He can attack the centre by means of ...c7-c5 and ...f7-f6.}) 6...
Nxd5 7. c3 c5 {Black should strike in the centre before White manages to
stabilize the position.} 8. dxc5 h6 9. Bh4 Nf4 10. Qa4 {This is the only way
to pose some problems.} ({After} 10. Nb3 {Black can play} Qc7 {[%cal Gf8d8]
